sting your pride.

306
00:16:18,870 --> 00:16:19,710
Let's go.

307
00:16:20,230 --> 00:16:21,080
Hurry.

308
00:16:21,080 --> 00:16:22,080
Stop tugging at me.

309
00:16:24,080 --> 00:16:25,150
Hurry up.

310
00:16:25,480 --> 00:16:26,320
Father,

311
00:16:26,590 --> 00:16:27,430
Mother.

312
00:16:27,550 --> 00:16:28,390
Qingzhao,

313
00:16:29,870 --> 00:16:31,120
