it back to him.

333
00:17:18,590 --> 00:17:19,430
Mingshu,

334
00:17:21,200 --> 00:17:22,640
you're a smart girl.

335
00:17:23,720 --> 00:17:24,920
The hairpin,

336
00:17:25,640 --> 00:17:27,160
the medicine,

337
00:17:27,830 --> 00:17:29,920
and his taking care you.

338
00:17:30,680 --> 00:17:32,790
Everyone can see that.

339
00:17:33,960 --> 00:17:35,680
If you keep silent,

340
00:17:36,270 --> 00:17:38,480
it's against reason
and sentiment.

341
00:17:41,030 --> 00:17:42,400
I always feel relaxed

342
00:17:43,030 --> 00:17:45,510
whenever I am with him.

343
00:17:45,880 --> 00:17:46,920
But I never think

344
00:17:47,750 --> 00:17:48,790
about other stuff.

345
00:17:49,720 --> 00:17:51,270
If you really like him,

346
00:17:51,680 --> 00:17:53,400
I'll bring you together.

347
00:17:54,030 --> 00:17:55,680
But if you hesitate,

348
00:17:56,070 --> 00:17:58,110
you should keep distance

349
00:17:58,640 --> 00:17:59,790
