he misunderstands you.

350
00:18:00,310 --> 00:18:02,750
It'll bring him pain.

351
00:18:05,510 --> 00:18:06,350
I got it.

352
00:18:08,240 --> 00:18:09,080
Good night.

353
00:18:24,790 --> 00:18:26,880
I know Qingzhao is kind

354
00:18:27,550 --> 00:18:29,440
and will be
a good husband.

355
00:18:30,310 --> 00:18:31,480
But I don't

356
00:18:32,240 --> 00:18:34,070
have a crush on him.

357
00:18:35,270 --> 00:18:37,030
And I never have
a crush on him

358
00:18:38,400 --> 00:18:40,110
