on the guy in my dream.

359
00:18:46,480 --> 00:18:47,880
You're so mysterious.

360
00:18:48,440 --> 00:18:49,510
What's the matter?

361
00:18:55,680 --> 00:18:56,520
After this tribulation,

362
00:18:57,510 --> 00:18:58,790
I figure out one thing.

363
00:19:00,880 --> 00:19:02,200
I can't lose Mingshu.

364
00:19:05,030 --> 00:19:05,870
Absolutely not.

365
00:19:07,400 --> 00:19:08,240
Well,

366
00:19:13,270 --> 00:19:14,400
as your friend,

367
00:19:14,790 --> 00:19:16,110
I support you.

368
00:19:16,480 --> 00:19:17,920
But Mingshu
is your sister.

369
00:19:18,550 --> 00:19:19,680
