it yourself.

370
00:19:19,680 --> 00:19:20,520
What will you do?

371
00:19:20,790 --> 00:19:21,720
I know.

372
00:19:22,830 --> 00:19:23,790
I asked for the pain.

373
00:19:25,790 --> 00:19:27,920
She said she dreamed
of the past.

374
00:19:28,790 --> 00:19:30,000
I hope I can

375
00:19:30,920 --> 00:19:32,510
restore her memory.

376
00:19:33,160 --> 00:19:34,270
Then I can walk

377
00:19:34,270 --> 00:19:35,270
to her openly.

378
00:19:37,110 --> 00:19:38,790
But you're her brother.

379
00:19:39,030 --> 00:19:40,400
You guys
can't be together

380
00:19:41,790 --> 00:19:43,240
unless you tell her
the truth.

381
00:19:43,790 --> 00:19:44,630
No way.

382
00:19:46,110 --> 00:19:47,200
If she knows

383
00:19:47,200 --> 00:19:49,070
all her family
died miserably,

384
00:19:49,550 --> 00:19:51,070
I don't know
what she'll do.

385
00:19:52,640 --> 00:19:53,880
I can't take that risk.

386
00:19:54,920 --> 00:19:55,760
Well,

387
00:19:58,400 --> 00:19:59,880
tell her she was adopted.

388
00:20:00,640 --> 00:20:01,550
After all,
she knows nothing

389
00:20:01,550 --> 00:20:02,390
about her past.

390
00:20:02,720 --> 00:20:04,070
This covers all bases!

391
00:20:04,240 --> 00:20:05,240
No,

392
00:20:05,590 --> 00:20:07,070
we should consider
her feelings.

393
00:20:07,830 --> 00:20:09,110
I can't be so selfish.

394
00:20:09,110 --> 00:20:10,270
Look at you,

395
00:20:10,550 --> 00:20:12,480
you denied
all the proposals.

396
00:20:12,640 --> 00:20:13,830
If you don't
stop hesitating,

397
00:20:13,830 --> 00:20:15,640
Mingshu will choose Qingzhao
over you.

398
00:20:15,960 --> 00:20:17,240
Then you'll regret.

399
00:20:19,070 --> 00:20:21,920
If she's not
into Qingzhao,

400
00:20:23,070 --> 00:20:24,920
I can take time
to look for a chance.

401
00:20:26,400 --> 00:20:27,640
But on one premise,

402
00:20:27,920 --> 00:20:29,000
not to hurt her.

403
00:20:32,140 --> 00:20:33,020
(Hualang Pavilion)

404
00:20:33,020 --> 00:20:34,270
Lady, come have a look.

405
00:20:34,480 --> 00:20:35,320
This way.

406
00:20:53,070 --> 00:20:53,910
Finally,

407
00:20:54,400 --> 00:20:56,110
my cousin gave it
to you.

408
00:20:58,220 --> 00:20:59,080
Mingshu,

409
00:20:59,200 --> 00:21:00,440
I've wanted to ask you.

410
00:21:00,830 --> 00:21:02,640
How do you feel

411
00:21:03,000 --> 00:21:04,640
about my cousin?

412
00:21:06,880 --> 00:21:08,640
I'm not sure.

413
00:21:09,030 --> 00:21:10,480
He's very into you.

414
00:21:10,480 --> 00:21:11,830
We all can tell.

415
00:21:11,960 --> 00:21:13,640
He took great
care of you

416
00:21:13,640 --> 00:21:14,830
when you were
in a coma.

417
00:21:14,830 --> 00:21:16,070
That was touching.

418
00:21:16,200 --> 00:21:17,880
If you can tie the knot,

419
00:21:18,110 --> 00:21:19,510
we'll feel happy for you.

420
00:21:19,750 --> 00:21:20,790
We wonder

421
00:21:20,790 --> 00:21:22,030
what you're
concerned about.

422
00:21:22,350 --> 00:21:23,720
Since we're friends,

423
00:21:24,030 --> 00:21:25,640
I won't keep this
from you.

424
00:21:26,750 --> 00:21:27,830
I treat Qingzhao

425
00:21:28,480 --> 00:21:29,880
