426
00:21:30,590 --> 00:21:32,830
Although I took marriage
into consideration,

427
00:21:33,400 --> 00:21:34,790
for a second thought,

428
00:21:34,960 --> 00:21:38,000
I don't have
a crush on him.

429
00:21:38,790 --> 00:21:41,070
I shouldn't mistake

430
00:21:41,070 --> 00:21:42,030
friendship for romance.

431
00:21:42,640 --> 00:21:43,550
What do you think?

432
00:21:43,720 --> 00:21:44,640
I'll go first.

433
00:21:47,720 --> 00:21:49,880
If you're a couple,

434
00:21:50,110 --> 00:21:51,550
you'll become my family.

435
00:21:52,480 --> 00:21:54,110
But it's up to you

436
00:21:54,440 --> 00:21:55,920
whether it'll work.

437
00:21:56,310 --> 00:21:58,350
Even if you're not
my sister-in-law.

438
00:21:58,480 --> 00:22:00,200
we're still besties.

439
00:22:01,270 --> 00:22:02,590
Wen'an, thank you.

440
00:22:03,400 --> 00:22:04,880
We'll support you

441
00:22:05,350 --> 00:22:06,590
whatever decisions
you make.

442
00:22:07,640 --> 00:22:08,750
Good to have you guys.

443
00:22:11,920 --> 00:22:13,400
The charity sale
is undergoing.

444
00:22:13,400 --> 00:22:14,480
Let's get back to work.

445
00:22:16,480 --> 00:22:17,320
Mingshu.

446
00:22:17,510 --> 00:22:18,350
Qing...

447
00:22:18,590 --> 00:22:19,430
Qingzhao,

448
00:22:19,830 --> 00:22:20,670
you're here.

449
00:22:21,110 --> 00:22:22,440
I have something
to tell you.

450
00:22:24,030 --> 00:22:25,110
We'll leave you

451
00:22:25,110 --> 00:22:26,110
guys alone.

452
00:22:28,480 --> 00:22:30,400
Qingzhao must be
very sad.

453
00:22:33,400 --> 00:22:35,720
It's been dry
these days.

454
00:22:36,270 --> 00:22:37,110
