455
00:22:37,550 --> 00:22:39,920
Since Madam Li
coughs a lot,

456
00:22:40,030 --> 00:22:41,880
I made this soup for her.

457
00:22:42,030 --> 00:22:42,870
Also for you.

458
00:22:44,590 --> 00:22:46,270
Madam Li, come on.

459
00:22:53,720 --> 00:22:55,000
Lady Zeng, don't mind it.

460
00:22:55,640 --> 00:22:58,240
