479
00:23:52,350 --> 00:23:53,270
Finish it all.

480
00:23:58,270 --> 00:23:59,440
There's a lot.

481
00:24:00,000 --> 00:24:00,880
Let's finish it.

482
00:24:02,440 --> 00:24:03,280
Qingzhao,

483
00:24:03,750 --> 00:24:05,030
thank you

484
00:24:05,030 --> 00:24:06,880
for saving me

485
00:24:07,200 --> 00:24:08,440
and taking care of me.

486
00:24:08,440 --> 00:24:09,640
I know everything.

487
00:24:09,750 --> 00:24:11,070
I really appreciate it.

488
00:24:11,350 --> 00:24:12,190
Mingshu,

489
00:24:12,790 --> 00:24:15,030
don't mention it.

490
00:24:16,160 --> 00:24:17,000
One more thing.

491
00:24:25,440 --> 00:24:26,280
This is

492
00:24:26,920 --> 00:24:28,070
the hibiscus hairpin

493
00:24:28,070 --> 00:24:30,030
