Hualang Pavilion.

494
00:24:30,400 --> 00:24:31,790
I know it's valuable

495
00:24:32,480 --> 00:24:33,680
and I can tell

496
00:24:33,680 --> 00:24:34,920
the meaning
behind it.

497
00:24:35,790 --> 00:24:36,630
But

498
00:24:37,070 --> 00:24:38,160
