527
00:26:06,480 --> 00:26:07,880
I won't complain.

528
00:26:10,310 --> 00:26:11,680
Thank you, Qingzhao.

529
00:26:16,680 --> 00:26:17,520
Well...

530
00:26:18,270 --> 00:26:19,480
