00:28:21,070 --> 00:28:21,910
Okay.

567
00:28:21,930 --> 00:28:23,960
And red bean soup.

568
00:28:23,980 --> 00:28:24,880
Sure.

569
00:28:24,880 --> 00:28:25,720
You came before?

570
00:28:26,880 --> 00:28:28,590
I did, with Qingzhao.

571
00:28:30,310 --> 00:28:31,750
Why would I choose
this shop?

572
00:28:33,640 --> 00:28:34,790
Buddy, what did you say?

573
00:28:35,880 --> 00:28:36,880
You said you wanted

574
00:28:36,880 --> 00:28:38,550
